  <para>
    <command>OOF.SegmentSelection.Select_From_Selected_Elements</command>
    provides three ways of selecting &sgmts; based on a pre-existing
    &elem; selection.  The two parameters <varname>internal</varname>
    and <varname>boundary</varname> control which &sgmts; will be
    selected.  If <varname>internal</varname> is true, then the
    &sgmts; that are shared by exactly two selected &elems; will be
    selected.  If <varname>boundary</varname> is true, then the
    &sgmts; that are part of only one selected &elem; will be
    selected.
  </para>

